product.title: Rainbow Butterfly Floral Gold-plated Adjustable Ring
product.body_html:
Affordable and durable rings ready to dazzle up your style

A simple yet charming ring that will brighten up your day. This ring features a lovely butterfly design with multicolored enamel and a floral touch. Made of high-quality brass with 18k gold plating, and is adjustable to fit almost all finger sizes.

This ring is a perfect gift for anyone who loves butterflies, and flowers, or just wants to add some fun to their look. A way to celebrate your joy and happiness.

  • Shape: Butterfly
  • Size: Adjustable
  • Metal Type: Brass
  • Material: 18K Real Gold-Plating
  • Category: Rings
  • Package includes: 1 Ring Only
  • Packaging: Rings do not come with the original box to protect the environment but they do come in a plastic bag. Let's save our planet together from unnecessary waste.
  • Maintenance: 18k gold-plated jewelry will not fade. If the color becomes darker, wash it with soap to restore the brightness. Do not wash your hands with the ring on. 

Elevate your jewelry collection today with rings from www.kawaiies.com!
